description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Alan Watts - Guided Meditation (Awakening The Mind)' from the channel Indigo Bliss.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Another video, in a series of more to come, that I believe really provides relief from perspective. Here is Alan Watts, a name which needs no introduction, sharing his method of obtaining self awareness. I then enhanced the audio quality, and paired it with a song that I felt was suitable and would sync nicely with his words.

We are all looking for a way to find our answers, which is why this video was made, and you are here watching it. All the best...IB

Thanks to dreamscene.org for the animation....
